                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8095" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0228</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2953 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“国货之光”如何持续发光？——贝泰妮 ESG 战略蓝图绘成记</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How does domestic brand Winona achieve sustainable development? -- The development of domestic brands based on ESG&#39;s strategic vision</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵书虹，杨越琴，杨雨婷，李琴，孔营营，杨兰，李晓光，李佳懿，杨敏，倪向丽</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南贝泰妮生物科技集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理论；可持续发展；战略选择；云南贝泰妮生物科技集团股份有限公司；微案例none</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG theory; Sustainable development; Strategic choice; Yunnan Botanee Biotechnology Group Co. LTD</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">近年来，ESG投资市场关注度日益高涨，ESG工作质量成为了继财务报表之后，更能体现企业发展潜力与格局的“全面体检报告”，也成为了中国本土企业的面临的新课题。本案例以云南贝泰妮生物科技集团股份有限公司（以下简称贝泰妮）为例，基于面临困境—ESG实践—践行收获—未来展望的思路，集中对贝泰妮发展面临困境、ESG战略选择与践行进行了深度分析。发现贝泰妮以ESG标准为指引的管理成绩显著，不仅实现经济效益与社会效益并行，也为国产化妆品行业的可持续发展树立了标杆，为相类似企业提供了战略决策参考借鉴。同时，目前我国企业ESG管理还处于初级阶段，还需企业共同发力进一步完善ESG管理。通过对本案例的学习与思考，可以使学生深入了解企业ESG管理的内涵与价值，帮助学生树立ESG理念，以及培养学生运用所学对ESG管理进行运用与拓展的能力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> In recent years, the attention of ESG investment market is increasing. The quality of ESG work has become a &quot;comprehensive physical examination report&quot; which can better reflect the development potential and pattern of enterprises after financial statements, and has also become a new topic faced by Chinese local enterprises. This case takes Yunnan Botanee Biotechnology Group Co., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as Botanee) as an example. Based on the thinking of dilemma -- ESG practice -- practicing harvest -- future prospect, this case focuses on in-depth analysis of Botanee&#39;s development dilemma and ESG strategy selection and practice. It is found that Botanee has achieved remarkable management results guided by ESG standards, which not only achieves parallel economic benefits and social benefits, but also sets a benchmark for the sustainable development of domestic cosmetics industry and provides strategic decision-making reference for similar enterprises. At the same time, at present, Chinese enterprises ESG management is still in the primary stage, so we need enterprises to work together to improve ESG management. Through the study and thinking of this case, students can have a deep understanding of the connotation and value of enterprise ESG management, help students establish the concept of ESG, and cultivate students&#39; ability to apply and expand ESG management with what they have learned.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">ESG理论；可持续商业模式；利益相关者理论；信号传递理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
                            </tr>
